Invocation Name: stephen hawking trivia
des:
Stephen Hawking Trivia can give you an interesting collection of facts about Stephen Hawking's life and you can also ask for some amazing quotes by Stephen Hawking.

Say,
"give me a fact" for an interesting fact of Stephen Hawking, and,
"give me a quote" for an amazing quote from Stephen Hawking.
